 Multiloop: Becoming THE TTRPG Campaign Management Platform

 Vision

 Replace Google Docs, compete with Kanka/World Anvil/Obsidian Portal, and become the only site worth using for TTRPG campaign management - from Session 0 pitch to ongoing play to
  campaign completion.

 NOT in scope: Virtual tabletop (VTT), battle maps, character stat management during combat, dice rolling, initiative tracking.

 IN scope: Everything around the table - campaign organization, session notes, world building, player collaboration, sharing, and AI-powered assistance that saves time without
 being "AI-y".

 ---
 What Already Exists (Verified)

 Template System - FULLY IMPLEMENTED

 - Works for all three content types (campaigns, characters, oneshots)
 - Publishing creates immutable snapshots with version management
 - "Save to Collection" is lightweight reference
 - "Start Playing" copies data into user's editable version
 - Attribution, update notifications, Session 0 ready flags all working
 - Future community marketplace infrastructure in place

 D&D Beyond / External Sheet Linking - ALREADY EXISTS

 - character_sheet_url field in vault_characters
 - character_links table for additional links (art, inspiration, etc.)
 - UI for adding links with type selection
 - Displayed across editor, viewer, mobile, presentation, share views
 - We do NOT store D&D stats - just link to external sources

