 The Big Features to Build

 1. Player Collaboration System (CRITICAL)

 The Problem: Currently campaigns are DM-only. Players can't contribute.

 The Solution: Multi-tiered access with invite flexibility.

 Invite Methods (equal options):
 - Email invite (magic link)
 - Discord invite (requires Discord auth setup)
 - Password-protected view link (for guests)

 Access Levels:
