 Session 0 Snapshot:
 - Automatically created when character joins campaign
 - Immutable preservation of original state
 - Player can "Fork from Session 0" to start fresh in new campaign
 - Some players want baggage, some want clean slate - support both

 Campaign character view:
 - Default: Summary card (name, portrait, brief description)
 - Click to drill down: Full detail view
 - If linked to vault: Shows all fields (editable by player)
 - If not linked: Shows campaign fields only
 - DM always sees their DM notes; players never do

 3. Secrets & Visibility System

 The Problem: No way to annotate shared content with DM-only info.

 The Solution: Triple-layer visibility with post-session reveal tracking.

 Important: Players watch VTT/tabletop during sessions, not Multiloop. Reveals happen verbally at the table. Multiloop just tracks what players CAN see when they browse.

 Visibility Layers:
