 Suggestion Feedback System:
 - Every suggestion has thumbs up/down buttons
 - Feedback stored and linked to existing feedback system
 - Helps measure AI quality without explicit reviews
 - Admin can see: "Timeline suggestions: 78% positive, NPC detection: 62% positive"

 Character Intelligence - Same pattern:
 - Backstory inconsistencies
 - Relationship suggestions
 - Missing fields
 - Arc tracking ("Your character has grown from X to Y")
 - Same ğŸ‘/ğŸ‘ feedback on each suggestion

