 Default 12 hours for founders - admin can adjust per tier.

 Why cooldowns over monthly limits:
 - "Available in 8 hours" is clearer than "3 runs left"
 - Naturally encourages batching updates
 - No gaming or saving up
 - Predictable for users

 Import is UNLIMITED - Priority is getting data onto the site.

