 No Visible "Credits":
 - Users don't see a credit counter
 - Just cooldown timers when applicable
 - Simple limit message if hit: "Limit reached. Available again on [date]"

 10. AI Admin Panel (CRITICAL)

 New admin section: /admin/ai-usage

 Purpose: Complete visibility into AI usage, costs, and effectiveness across the entire site.

