 Admin Controls

 Model Selection (existing, verify working):
 - Toggle between Gemini Pro 3, Gemini Flash 3, etc.
 - Apply site-wide instantly
 - Per-operation model override (future)

 Cooldown Configuration:
 - Edit cooldown hours per tier
 - Edit cooldown per Intelligence type
 - Changes apply site-wide immediately

 Per-User View:
 - Search/filter users
 - See individual user's AI usage
 - Cost attributed to user
 - Usage patterns

