 - Model comparison: Bar charts side-by-side
 - User leaderboard: Top users by usage/cost
 - Acceptance heatmap: Which suggestion types perform best

 11. Tutorials & Guidance

 The Problem: Features exist but users don't know how to use them effectively.

 The Solution: Contextual help throughout the entire site that guides WORKFLOWS, not just features.

 Guidance Philosophy

 Wrong approach (feature-focused):
 "You can add timeline events here"

 Right approach (workflow-focused):
 "Timeline events track your campaign's key moments. Add them manually, or let Campaign Intelligence suggest them from your session notes."

 Guidance Types
