 ---
 Out of Scope

 - VTT / battle maps with tokens
 - Dice rolling
 - Initiative tracking in campaigns
 - Character stat tracking during combat
 - Full calendar system (maybe v2)
 - Discord bot (future)
 - Offline mode
 - D&D Beyond API integration (they don't allow it)

 ---
 Critical Files to Modify

 Campaign System

 - src/app/(dashboard)/campaigns/[id]/ - Add dashboard route
 - src/components/campaigns/ - Dashboard widgets, member management
 - src/types/database.ts - New types for campaign_members, secrets, etc.

 Character System

 - src/components/vault/CharacterEditor.tsx - Campaign linking UI
 - src/app/(dashboard)/vault/ - Claiming flow
 - src/app/api/characters/ - Linking/claiming APIs

 Oneshot System

 - src/app/(dashboard)/oneshots/[id]/page.tsx - Structured content
 - src/app/(dashboard)/oneshots/[id]/run/page.tsx - Replace with Present mode
 - New components for NPCs, encounters, locations

 Intelligence System

 - src/app/(dashboard)/campaigns/[id]/intelligence/ - Review hub UI with feedback
 - src/app/(dashboard)/vault/[id]/intelligence/ - Character intelligence with feedback
 - src/app/api/intelligence/ - Suggestion generation with logging
 - New: Cooldown checking middleware
 - New: Suggestion feedback API

 AI Admin Panel

 - src/app/(dashboard)/admin/ai-usage/ - New admin page
 - src/components/admin/ai/ - Dashboard widgets, charts, tables
 - src/app/api/admin/ai/ - Usage stats, cost tracking, config APIs
 - src/lib/ai/ - Logging middleware, cooldown enforcement

 Import System

 - src/app/api/vault/import*/ - Add import session tracking
 - src/components/vault/import/ - Funnel tracking integration

 Sharing & Auth

 - src/lib/supabase/ - Discord auth setup
 - src/app/api/invites/ - New invite system

 Tutorials & Guidance

 - src/components/guidance/ - Reusable tip components
 - src/hooks/useGuidance.ts - Track what user has seen
 - Empty state components across all feature areas